%% Architecture diagram for EasyMoto
flowchart LR
  C[Customer App] -->|create order| DB[(Firebase Realtime DB /orders)]
  DB -->|onCreate| CF[Cloud Function autoDispatchOnOrderCreate]
  CF -->|query| RIDERS[/riders/ (lat,lng,available)]
  CF -->|Distance Matrix| GMAP[Google Distance Matrix API]
  GMAP --> CF
  CF -->|transaction| RIDER_NODE[/riders/{riderId}]
  CF -->|update| DB
  CF -->|notify| NOTIF[FCM / Expo Push]
  RIDER_APP[Rider App] -->|location updates| DB
  ADMIN[Admin Dashboard] -->|reads| DB
  ANALYTICS[BigQuery / Data Studio] -->|ingest| DB
